caption.title: Summary of the VACV ligands that were detected by MS/MS analysis in the rVACV-CHIKV infected cells.

fn.p: a The monoisotopic ion mass in amu.
b The difference between nominal and experimentally detected monoisotopic ions in ppm.
c Asterisks indicate oxidation of Met. The minimal core for binding of D12 99–111 ligand to respective HLA class I molecule is bolded.
d HLA-A*03:01 and/or HLA-C*01:02 assignments (calculated as percentile rank < 5) are bolded.
e and f Theoretical affinity to HLA of the CHIKV ligands calculated as percentile rank from the Immuno Epitope Database (IEDB) or the NetMHCpan servers, respectively. (-), no binding.
